# FX Market Research agent — enables Claude-generated commentary + per-pair signals.
# Without it, live rates still load and signals fall back to a rule-based read.
# Get a key at https://console.anthropic.com → set the same var in Vercel project env.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# Enables LIVE economic calendar + FX news headlines via Apify:
#   - gochujang/economic-calendar-tracker (ForexFactory, free)
#   - cloud9_ai/investing-news-scraper (Investing.com, ~$0.002/headline)
# News headlines ground Claude's commentary in real events. Without the token,
# the calendar falls back to the curated list and commentary runs without news.
# Get a token at https://console.apify.com/account/integrations
APIFY_TOKEN=apify_api_...
